<refentry version="5.0-subset Scilab" xml:id="getIPCVpath" xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
<refnamediv><refname>getIPCVpath</refname><refpurpose>Return the IPCV installation folder.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>path = getIPCVpath()</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>getIPCVpath</function> returns the absolute root folder of the currently loaded IPCV toolbox.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting><![CDATA[
path = getIPCVpath();
image = imread(fullfile(path, "images", "baboon.png"));
]]></programlisting></refsection>
